installing putty on raspberry pi.
	sudo apt-get install putty -y

inatalling virtual keyboard.
	sudo apt-get install matchbox-keyboard

installing the latest updates on raspberry pi.
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get upgrade
	sudo apt-get install rpi-update

installing ssh to get a remote login to command line.

installing firmata library for python and its modules by pip module manager. 
	sudo apt-get install python-serial mercurial
	pip install firmata